268
00:20:17,480 --> 00:20:19,320
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

269
00:20:29,240 --> 00:20:30,000
Get lost.

270
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:39,080
Wu Shanlong!

271
00:20:40,280 --> 00:20:41,160
Stop!

272
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:54,840
What the heck?

273
00:21:03,480 --> 00:21:04,320
Is this his car?

274
00:21:05,520 --> 00:21:08,040
He! He's here!

275
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:11,240
I've locked the door to the stairs!
Are there any more exits?

276
00:21:11,320 --> 00:21:12,600
The parking lot entrance.

277
00:21:13,120 --> 00:21:15,960
The parking lot entrance
was opened last week!

278
00:21:16,040 --> 00:21:18,160
He might be able to exit from there!

279
00:21:20,600 --> 00:21:21,640
Stop!

280
00:21:22,720 --> 00:21:23,760
Catch him!

281
00:21:27,200 --> 00:21:28,840
Move! Move!

282
00:21:29,840 --> 00:21:31,040
Move!

283
00:21:31,120 --> 00:21:32,600
What are you doing?

284
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:34,560
He went that way!

285
00:22:25,760 --> 00:22:26,880
After him!

286
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:41,720
He!

287
00:23:44,040 --> 00:23:44,960
He!

288
00:23:47,960 --> 00:23:49,040
He!

289
00:23:54,320 --> 00:23:55,160
He!

290
00:23:58,920 --> 00:24:00,400
Quick, call an ambulance!

291
00:24:01,520 --> 00:24:03,120
Stay awake, He!

292
00:24:07,840 --> 00:24:08,680
He!

293
00:24:10,080 --> 00:24:11,360
Stay awake, He!

294
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:22,320
He!

295
00:24:54,120 --> 00:24:56,080
The steel rod pierced his lung

296
00:24:56,160 --> 00:24:57,400
and broke his rib.

297
00:24:58,080 --> 00:25:00,360
Thankfully, Officer He is lucky.

298
00:25:00,440 --> 00:25:01,360
A few centimeters above,

299
00:25:02,600 --> 00:25:04,200
and it'd have pierced his heart.

300
00:25:04,280 --> 00:25:05,880
The consequences could've been worse.

301
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:09,240
You must do your best to treat him.

302
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:11,920
There mustn't be any complications.

303
00:25:12,520 --> 00:25:15,600
He is the hero of the police force.

304
00:25:15,680 --> 00:25:16,600
Don't worry.

305
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:18,600
Thank you.

306
00:25:27,520 --> 00:25:28,440
Sir!

307
00:25:31,520 --> 00:25:32,440
Sir!

308
00:25:36,240 --> 00:25:37,200
Sir!

309
00:25:43,400 --> 00:25:45,000
Are you all right, sir?

310
00:25:54,400 --> 00:25:55,280
He.

311
00:25:59,160 --> 00:26:01,760
He. Are you all right, He?

312
00:26:08,320 --> 00:26:09,160
FOLDER

313
00:26:10,760 --> 00:26:12,560
- Be careful.
- Be careful.

314
00:26:18,080 --> 00:26:19,160
Dad.

315
00:26:22,680 --> 00:26:23,720
I'm fine.

316
00:26:25,560 --> 00:26:26,400
Are you really fine?

317
00:26:27,320 --> 00:26:29,320
I said I'm fine.

318
00:26:34,120 --> 00:26:35,080
Anyway, He,

319
00:26:35,160 --> 00:26:38,280
why did you suddenly think
of bringing Xiaohe

320
00:26:38,360 --> 00:26:40,280
to Yuanlongli's internet cafe
to search for clues?

321
00:26:41,560 --> 00:26:43,600
Ran brought us there.

322
00:26:54,160 --> 00:26:55,000
Ran.

323
00:26:55,080 --> 00:26:57,320
Don't just stand there.

324
00:26:57,840 --> 00:26:59,360
Tell everyone about it.

325
00:27:01,200 --> 00:27:02,080
No way.

326
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:08,480
Yes.

327
00:27:08,560 --> 00:27:10,640
Did you hear what he just said?

328
00:27:12,600 --> 00:27:15,760
I… What did he just say?

329
00:27:15,840 --> 00:27:17,840
Stop playing dumb.

330
00:27:20,000 --> 00:27:21,240
He was scolding you.

331
00:27:21,320 --> 00:27:23,520
He said you were biased towards Qu Dahai.

332
00:27:24,120 --> 00:27:26,080
Xiaohe found the lead,

333
00:27:26,680 --> 00:27:28,520
but you gave Qu Dahai the case

334
00:27:28,600 --> 00:27:31,000
and even stopped Xiaohe
from joining the task force.

335
00:27:31,080 --> 00:27:34,200
Is the criminal department
trying to steal credit too?

336
00:27:34,720 --> 00:27:35,520
Captain,

337
00:27:35,600 --> 00:27:37,160
I did it for Xiaohe's sake.

338
00:27:37,240 --> 00:27:40,320
Wasn't Xiaohe kidnapped
when she was a child?

339
00:27:40,400 --> 00:27:42,280
I was afraid that she
might relive those memories

340
00:27:42,360 --> 00:27:43,560
after joining the task force.

341
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:46,120
What if it triggered… What you call it…

342
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:48,760
Hush. I can't hear him.

343
00:27:55,920 --> 00:27:56,760
You hear that?

344
00:27:56,840 --> 00:27:58,080
He's scolding you.

345
00:27:58,840 --> 00:27:59,680
Are you talking to me?

346
00:27:59,760 --> 00:28:01,600
Captain Ran said

347
00:28:01,680 --> 00:28:04,240
the internet cafe owner you arrested

348
00:28:04,320 --> 00:28:07,120
wasn't a kidnapping suspect.

349
00:28:07,200 --> 00:28:09,760
You are only wasting your time
by interrogating him.

350
00:28:09,840 --> 00:28:13,920
Also, Ran taught you
the Tremaux Algorithm.

351
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:16,120
Shouldn't you provide guidance
to Xiaohe now?

352
00:28:19,760 --> 00:28:21,040
Dad,

353
00:28:21,120 --> 00:28:23,160
you've had a long day.

354
00:28:23,240 --> 00:28:24,080
Let's go home.

355
00:28:25,320 --> 00:28:27,760
Uncle Ran still has a train to catch.

356
00:28:49,680 --> 00:28:50,520
He Xiaohe.

357
00:28:51,400 --> 00:28:52,240
Yes.

358
00:28:53,160 --> 00:28:54,440
As long as you won't affect

359
00:28:54,960 --> 00:28:57,040
the Special Task Force's investigation,

360
00:28:57,120 --> 00:28:58,080
I will give you special permission

361
00:28:58,160 --> 00:28:59,840
to assist in the investigation
of Han Zi'ang's case.

362
00:29:00,600 --> 00:29:02,320
However, you must report all your actions

363
00:29:02,400 --> 00:29:04,040
to the team leader of the task force.

364
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:07,920
Thank you, Captain.

365
00:29:08,000 --> 00:29:09,440
- Hold on…
- Enough.

366
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:13,920
Captain, many parents are outside.

367
00:29:23,760 --> 00:29:25,960
I'm warning you. Don't pull
this trick often in the future.

368
00:29:41,440 --> 00:29:43,000
Train harder

369
00:29:43,840 --> 00:29:45,800
if you want to outwit me.

370
00:30:35,360 --> 00:30:36,920
CRIMINAL DEPARTMENT OFFICE

371
00:31:01,040 --> 00:31:01,880
He.

372
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:06,960
He. You're awake.

373
00:31:07,040 --> 00:31:09,920
- Let me call a doctor.
- Wait. There's no rush.

374
00:31:10,920 --> 00:31:12,280
Water.

375
00:31:24,080 --> 00:31:24,960
Right away.

376
00:31:34,440 --> 00:31:35,440
How's that?

377
00:31:43,240 --> 00:31:44,200
Here.

378
00:31:49,840 --> 00:31:50,800
Brat,

379
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:52,720
are you trying to scald me?

380
00:31:53,840 --> 00:31:54,840
Let me add some cold water.

381
00:31:54,920 --> 00:31:56,240
No need.

382
00:31:57,640 --> 00:31:59,800
- Then, I'll go and find a doctor.
- Wait.

383
00:32:02,120 --> 00:32:02,960
Talk to me about the case.

384
00:32:04,720 --> 00:32:06,040
Where's Wu Shanlong?

385
00:32:07,320 --> 00:32:08,840
He was pierced by steel rods

386
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:10,960
and couldn't be resuscitated. He is dead.

387
00:32:17,720 --> 00:32:21,000
The people in the forensic department
found a small amount

388
00:32:21,080 --> 00:32:23,080
of human bone samples
in the bathroom's drain.

389
00:32:23,720 --> 00:32:25,160
After examination,

390
00:32:25,240 --> 00:32:27,880
it matches the DNA
found on Xu Zhihong's hair

391
00:32:27,960 --> 00:32:28,800
collected at Xu's apartment.

392
00:32:29,640 --> 00:32:30,560
Moreover,

393
00:32:30,640 --> 00:32:33,160
the skin samples found in the blue heels

394
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:35,000
also match Xu Meng's DNA.

395
00:32:35,080 --> 00:32:37,120
Combined with Wu Zhengxiong's

396
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:39,000
and Hu Anping's testimony…

397
00:32:39,080 --> 00:32:41,000
In 1997, Wu Shanlong

398
00:32:41,080 --> 00:32:42,440
hired Wolfie to murder someone.

399
00:32:42,520 --> 00:32:43,960
Wu Shanlong said

400
00:32:44,480 --> 00:32:47,360
he went and did the deed himself.

401
00:32:48,080 --> 00:32:48,960
We can basically confirm

402
00:32:50,040 --> 00:32:52,280
that Wu Shanlong is the murderer
of Xu Meng and her father.

403
00:32:54,280 --> 00:32:55,240
Are there any accomplices?

404
00:32:56,040 --> 00:32:56,960
None has been found at the moment.

405
00:32:59,240 --> 00:33:00,160
What about the motive?

406
00:33:01,080 --> 00:33:03,320
According to the information
we have currently,

407
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:06,440
my guess is that Wu Shanlong
had a strong urge to control women

408
00:33:06,520 --> 00:33:08,960
due to his physiological defect.

409
00:33:09,040 --> 00:33:11,160
He visited the foot massage parlor
frequently with Song Qingsong.

410
00:33:11,240 --> 00:33:14,000
<i>He had his eyes on Xu Meng</i>
<i>and wanted her to himself.</i>

411
00:33:14,080 --> 00:33:14,920
MUSE FOOT MASSAGE

412
00:33:15,000 --> 00:33:16,720
<i>After Song Qingsong decided</i>
<i>to hire him to murder the victims,</i>

413
00:33:17,560 --> 00:33:19,480
<i>Wu Shanlong lied</i>
<i>and used Wolfie as a scapegoat.</i>

414
00:33:19,560 --> 00:33:22,080
<i>He then purposely helped</i>
<i>Xu Meng and her father</i>

415
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:24,640
<i>to disappear to escape debt.</i>

416
00:33:24,720 --> 00:33:27,840
<i>Xu Meng thought Wu Shanlong</i>
<i>helped her out of kindness.</i>

417
00:33:27,920 --> 00:33:30,040
<i>To her surprise, he was actually trying</i>
<i>to take her by force</i>

418
00:33:30,120 --> 00:33:31,200
<i>after she successfully escaped.</i>

419
00:33:31,800 --> 00:33:34,200
Wu Shanlong faced resistance
from Xu Meng and her father,

420
00:33:34,280 --> 00:33:37,240
and he was afraid of Song Qingsong
finding out about his plan.

421
00:33:37,320 --> 00:33:38,640
In the end,

422
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:40,880
he killed them both.

423
00:33:49,040 --> 00:33:50,320
Unfortunately,

424
00:33:51,640 --> 00:33:53,520
we couldn't find Xu Meng's body.

425
00:33:57,120 --> 00:34:03,120
NANSHAN BRANCH
BUILDING NO. 1, INPATIENT DEPARTMENT

426
00:34:10,679 --> 00:34:11,520
Xiaohe.

427
00:34:13,960 --> 00:34:15,000
Xiaohe!

428
00:34:32,239 --> 00:34:33,320
Mrs. He,

429
00:34:33,400 --> 00:34:34,800
you're right on time.

430
00:34:34,880 --> 00:34:35,920
He just woke up.

431
00:34:40,520 --> 00:34:41,360
Take a seat.

432
00:34:58,520 --> 00:34:59,440
Xiaohe.

433
00:35:09,880 --> 00:35:11,120
I've not seen you for ages.

434
00:35:12,040 --> 00:35:12,960
You've lost weight.

435
00:35:14,720 --> 00:35:16,240
You are in such bad shape.

436
00:35:16,320 --> 00:35:17,320
It's fine.

437
00:35:18,200 --> 00:35:19,360
Just a minor wound.

438
00:35:23,360 --> 00:35:24,200
Xiaohe,

439
00:35:24,920 --> 00:35:27,600
I've achieved something huge this time.

440
00:35:27,680 --> 00:35:31,360
The criminal used a steel rod this long
to stab me at this place,

441
00:35:32,040 --> 00:35:34,160
and I didn't even let out a groan.

442
00:35:34,240 --> 00:35:36,440
I even beat up the criminal.

443
00:35:40,320 --> 00:35:43,160
So you risked your life
just to achieve something.

444
00:35:43,880 --> 00:35:45,440
You are no longer young.

445
00:35:45,520 --> 00:35:46,880
In the future,

446
00:35:47,560 --> 00:35:49,480
you must take good care of yourself.

447
00:36:26,320 --> 00:36:27,760
I've talked to you about this.

448
00:36:40,600 --> 00:36:42,280
DIVORCE AGREEMENT

449
00:36:47,440 --> 00:36:49,320
Our marriage has become like this

450
00:36:49,840 --> 00:36:51,280
for a while now.

451
00:36:52,160 --> 00:36:54,080
It's bad for everyone if this goes on.

452
00:36:55,400 --> 00:36:56,960
Why not just let it go

453
00:36:57,720 --> 00:36:58,840
and end it cleanly?

454
00:37:09,360 --> 00:37:11,840
Actually, I've been trying to talk
to you about this.

455
00:37:12,840 --> 00:37:14,320
But I've been busy with the investigation.

456
00:37:16,360 --> 00:37:17,200
Give me a pen.

457
00:37:39,920 --> 00:37:43,080
HUSBAND'S SIGNATURE
WIFE'S SIGNATURE: SUN YUN

458
00:37:47,320 --> 00:37:48,360
What's wrong?

459
00:37:51,600 --> 00:37:54,760
CUSTODY OF THE CHILD, HE XIAOHE
GOES TO THE WIFE

460
00:37:56,480 --> 00:37:58,840
I'll soon transfer
to the provincial headquarters.

461
00:37:58,920 --> 00:38:00,040
I'll bring Xiaohe with me.

462
00:38:00,120 --> 00:38:03,240
This is better for her.
Look at you right now.

463
00:38:03,320 --> 00:38:05,320
How can you even take care of her?

464
00:38:09,880 --> 00:38:12,520
Xiaohe is becoming more rebellious now.

465
00:38:12,600 --> 00:38:14,040
If she stays here,

466
00:38:14,120 --> 00:38:16,680
it won't be too long
until she goes astray.

467
00:38:17,680 --> 00:38:19,600
You don't need to pay alimony.

468
00:38:20,120 --> 00:38:22,080
I can support her on my own.

469
00:38:22,160 --> 00:38:23,640
If you miss her,

470
00:38:23,720 --> 00:38:25,840
you may visit her at any time.
I won't stop you.

471
00:38:30,440 --> 00:38:31,840
Do you hear me?

472
00:38:33,600 --> 00:38:34,600
He Yuanhang.

473
00:38:36,760 --> 00:38:38,320
He Yuanhang!

474
00:38:41,480 --> 00:38:43,040
I don't object to the divorce.

475
00:38:43,560 --> 00:38:46,440
We all want to seek happiness,
and I have nothing to say about that.

476
00:38:46,520 --> 00:38:48,040
Don't use me as an excuse in the future.

477
00:38:48,120 --> 00:38:50,240
I'm sick of hearing,
"It's for Xiaohe's sake."

478
00:38:51,480 --> 00:38:53,120
I'll decide how I live my life.

479
00:38:53,640 --> 00:38:54,480
I'm not going to the provincial capital.

480
00:38:54,560 --> 00:38:57,520
Xiaohe. The adults are talking.
Don't cause any trouble.

481
00:38:58,160 --> 00:39:00,120
The adults also shouldn't cause
any trouble for the child.

482
00:39:00,200 --> 00:39:01,680
The schools in the provincial capital
are so much better

483
00:39:01,760 --> 00:39:02,800
than the ones in Weiyang.

484
00:39:02,880 --> 00:39:05,920
Attending university or studying abroad
will be so much easier in the future.

485
00:39:06,000 --> 00:39:08,000
Don't you like music?

486
00:39:08,080 --> 00:39:10,440
England. The United States. France.

487
00:39:10,520 --> 00:39:12,200
No matter where you want to go,
I'll also support you.

488
00:39:12,280 --> 00:39:13,680
I don't need anyone to decide for me.

489
00:39:13,760 --> 00:39:15,960
He Xiaohe. I am your guardian.

490
00:39:16,040 --> 00:39:17,200
As long as you are still a minor,

491
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:19,480
you need my consent
before you make your decisions.

492
00:39:19,560 --> 00:39:20,720
This is non-negotiable.

493
00:39:20,800 --> 00:39:23,000
If that's the case,
it's also non-negotiable for me.

494
00:39:23,080 --> 00:39:24,040
I'm following Dad.

495
00:39:24,960 --> 00:39:27,800
Look at her. She's really stubborn,

496
00:39:27,880 --> 00:39:30,120
just like you.
She won't be able to turn good.

497
00:39:51,840 --> 00:39:54,120
CUSTODY OF THE CHILD, HE XIAOHE
GOES TO THE HUSBAND

498
00:40:04,600 --> 00:40:08,200
HUSBAND'S SIGNATURE: HE

499
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:33,920
What is it? You don't want her to leave?

500
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:40,400
Xiaohe, I have raised an amazing daughter.

501
00:40:41,000 --> 00:40:42,680
- Give me a hug.
- Don't be so full of yourself.

502
00:40:42,760 --> 00:40:45,560
Not leaving with Mom
has nothing to do with you.

503
00:40:46,720 --> 00:40:47,560
What do you mean?

504
00:40:47,640 --> 00:40:50,280
My friends, my band,

505
00:40:50,360 --> 00:40:51,440
and my rock career are all in Weiyang.

506
00:40:51,520 --> 00:40:52,800
Listen now.

507
00:40:52,880 --> 00:40:54,560
Leave me alone in the future.

508
00:40:54,640 --> 00:40:56,120
But I am your only parent now.

509
00:40:56,200 --> 00:40:57,400
You don't agree?

510
00:40:57,920 --> 00:40:59,800
Mom just left.
I'll call her back right away.

511
00:40:59,880 --> 00:41:01,320
I agree.

512
00:41:05,600 --> 00:41:06,680
I agree.

513
00:41:07,680 --> 00:41:08,800
Take good care of yourself.

514
00:41:09,880 --> 00:41:11,240
I still have lessons in the afternoon.

515
00:42:26,400 --> 00:42:30,480
Family is a strange thing.

516
00:42:33,280 --> 00:42:35,400
If the family is intact,

517
00:42:36,640 --> 00:42:38,400
people dig it

518
00:42:40,520 --> 00:42:42,760
until there's a hole.

519
00:42:43,800 --> 00:42:45,080
If it isn't intact,

520
00:42:47,320 --> 00:42:49,000
people will do their best to repair it.

521
00:42:50,600 --> 00:42:51,640
They will even

522
00:42:52,520 --> 00:42:55,520
do something as stupid
as repairing a golden bowl

523
00:42:56,600 --> 00:42:57,640
with a piece of tile.

524
00:43:26,840 --> 00:43:27,960
What is it?

525
00:43:29,000 --> 00:43:29,800
Take a guess.

526
00:43:33,000 --> 00:43:33,840
No.

527
00:43:43,200 --> 00:43:45,480
CERTIFICATE OF HONOR

528
00:43:45,560 --> 00:43:46,760
"In the June 30th case,

529
00:43:46,840 --> 00:43:50,080
Officer He Yuanhang demonstrated
keen investigative thinking,

530
00:43:50,160 --> 00:43:53,160
exceptional judgment,
a strong sense of responsibility,

531
00:43:53,240 --> 00:43:55,240
and extensive investigative experience.

532
00:43:55,320 --> 00:43:58,040
He made significant contributions
in solving the case.

533
00:44:00,040 --> 00:44:02,040
To commend his exemplary performance
and promote integrity,

534
00:44:02,120 --> 00:44:03,480
in accordance
with the People's Police Rewards

535
00:44:03,560 --> 00:44:04,920
and Punishments Regulations,

536
00:44:05,000 --> 00:44:06,600
it is submitted to the Provincial
Public Security Department

537
00:44:06,680 --> 00:44:10,080
that Officer He Yuanhang should be awarded
a second-class individual merit."

538
00:44:17,480 --> 00:44:20,160
The police station specifically
requested me to give it to you in person.

539
00:44:22,520 --> 00:44:25,120
SECOND-CLASS MERIT MEDAL
OF THE MINISTRY OF PUBLIC SECURITY OF PRC

540
00:44:28,960 --> 00:44:30,960
NAME: HE YUANHANG
MEDAL: SECOND-CLASS MERIT

541
00:44:35,440 --> 00:44:37,240
I get custody of my daughter

542
00:44:38,640 --> 00:44:40,120
and the second-class merit.

543
00:44:41,000 --> 00:44:42,120
Let's see

544
00:44:43,080 --> 00:44:44,440
who dares call me
a good-for-nothing again.

545
00:44:47,800 --> 00:44:50,600
What are you doing?
I'm not done admiring it.

546
00:44:56,160 --> 00:44:57,560
Once you recover,

547
00:44:57,640 --> 00:44:59,520
you must take your medications
for your condition on time.

548
00:44:59,600 --> 00:45:01,680
It's time to quit drinking cola.

549
00:45:01,760 --> 00:45:03,800
The same goes for cigarettes,
alcohol, and fatty meat.

550
00:45:04,400 --> 00:45:07,120
- The doctor even mentioned to--
- Enough.

551
00:45:07,200 --> 00:45:09,840
Stop nagging beside me. All right?

552
00:45:09,920 --> 00:45:11,000
You're so annoying.

553
00:45:11,520 --> 00:45:13,800
Go back and keep working, Deputy Captain.

554
00:45:30,040 --> 00:45:31,120
He.

555
00:45:31,200 --> 00:45:33,360
If you didn't push me away,

556
00:45:33,440 --> 00:45:37,000
I'd probably be the one lying here now.

557
00:45:39,200 --> 00:45:43,040
I told you not to nag. All right?

558
00:45:45,040 --> 00:45:46,280
Do you think I did it for you?

559
00:45:48,040 --> 00:45:49,680
I did it for myself.

560
00:45:49,760 --> 00:45:51,960
If I let my apprentice get hurt,

561
00:45:52,040 --> 00:45:55,120
it'll only make me look bad
as your mentor.

562
00:45:55,200 --> 00:45:56,800
It shows how incapable I am.

563
00:45:57,400 --> 00:45:58,800
Go away.

564
00:45:59,680 --> 00:46:00,960
Don't disturb my rest.

565
00:46:44,080 --> 00:46:45,040
I'm leaving,

566
00:46:46,080 --> 00:46:46,960
sir.
